| bits | trait                                                   | shift |
| ---- | ------------------------------------------------------- | ----- |
| 1    | dark mode                                               | 30    |
| 3    | layer: preflight, global, components, utilities, css    | 27    |
| 1    | screens: is this a responsive variation of a rule       | 26    |
| 4    | responsive based on min-width, max-width or width       | 22    |
| 4    | at-rules                                                | 18    |
| 18   | pseudo and group variants                               | 0     |

